metadata.name: SF #1
metadata.description:
Suki is a human-elf sapien hybrid, a member of the RED Special Forces, and a frontline soldier who fights on the front lines. As an elite fronter with the codename "Ice Queen", also known as the "Killer angel", she has always been cheeful towards her sisters and joined their special elit force called the "Killer angels". They are beautiful and dangerous, vixens in the truest sense of the word. RUN!

This collection contains a total of 3 series. 
SF, Killer Angels and Vixens
